# ── AUTHENTICATION ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Login (Get Token)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "sam@jitims.com",
  "password": "admin123"
}

# ── BORROW ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Create Borrow Request (change equipmentId to an available one)
POST {{baseUrl}}/borrow
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "equipmentId": 1,
  "expectedReturn": "2026-07-30",
  "notes": "For testing"
}

### Approve Borrow Request (change 1 to actual borrow record ID)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/borrow/1/approve
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Return Equipment (change 1 to actual borrow record ID)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/borrow/1/return
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "returnCondition": "GOOD"
}

# ── NOTIFICATIONS ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Get My Notifications
GET {{baseUrl}}/notifications
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Only Unresolved Notifications
GET {{baseUrl}}/notifications?unresolved=true
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Resolve a Notification (change 1 to actual notification ID)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/notifications/1/resolve
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}